<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Subscription Restricted</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0f172a;
      padding: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 32px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #7f1d1d;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    p {
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 24px;
    }
    .restricted-box {
      background-color: #fef2f2;
      border: 2px dashed #f87171;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .restricted-title {
      color: #991b1b;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .restricted-desc {
      color: #7f1d1d;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    .btn {
      background-color: #dc2626;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 24px 32px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    }
    .footer-text {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">SaaS Subscriptions</div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Subscription Suspended / Restricted</h1>
        <p>Hello {{customerName}},</p>
        <p>We're sorry to inform you that after 5 unsuccessful payment attempts, your premium subscription has been restricted or downgraded to the Free tier.</p>
        
        <div class="restricted-box">
          <div class="restricted-title">Account Status: Restricted</div>
          <div class="restricted-desc">Unpaid Invoice Reference: {{invoiceNumber}}</div>
        </div>

        <p>To restore access to all features and seats, please log in to your account, resolve your billing issues, and reactivate your paid subscription plan.</p>

        <div class="btn-container">
          <a href="https://enterprise-saas-billing.com/billing/settings" class="btn">Manage Billing Details</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p class="footer-text">
          &copy; 2026 SaaS Inc. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
